#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:4
msgid "三维场景"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:6
msgid ""
"在 JAnim 中，每个坐标都有三个分量 ``[x, y, z]`` ，在我们之前接触的二维场景中，我们只需要用到其中的前两个分量，当我们进入三"
"维场景后，第三个分量就会发挥作用"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:8
msgid ""
"在这之前，我们要先了解一下在三维空间中的摄像机旋转，以方便我们观察；在了解了摄像机旋转之后，我们便会进一步展开有关三维场景"
"的内容"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:11
msgid "在三维空间中旋转摄像机"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:13
msgid "在 :ref:`camera_usage` 这节中，我们使用了 :meth:`~.Cmpt_CameraPoints.rotate` 方法来旋转摄像机"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:15
msgid "这个方法还有一个参数 ``axis`` 即旋转轴，这个参数默认值为 ``OUT`` ，在这种情况下我们的摄像机只会在二维平面中旋转"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:17
msgid "我们如果改变这个参数，便可以在三维空间中旋转摄像机，从而呈现三维画面："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:13
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"# 画面中的主要元素：一个三维坐标轴以及一个在二维平面内的方形\n"
"\n"
"axes = ThreeDAxes(\n"
"    (-4, 4), (-4, 4), (-4, 4),\n"
"    axis_config={\n"
"        'include_tip': True\n"
"    }\n"
")\n"
"square = Square()\n"
"\n"
"# 用于演示的箭头和文字\n"
"\n"
"vec1 = Vector(RIGHT, color=YELLOW)\n"
"vec2 = Vector(OUT, color=YELLOW)\n"
"\n"
"txt1 = Text('axis=RIGHT', font_size=16, color=YELLOW)\n"
"txt1.points.next_to(vec1, UR, buff=SMALL_BUFF)\n"
"txt2 = Text('axis=OUT', font_size=16, color=YELLOW)\n"
"txt2.points.next_to(vec2, OUT, buff=SMALL_BUFF)\n"
"\n"
"group1 = Group(vec1, txt1)\n"
"group2 = Group(vec2, txt2)\n"
"\n"
"# 动画过程\n"
"\n"
"self.show(axes, square)\n"
"\n"
"self.play(FadeIn(group1))\n"
"self.play(\n"
"    self.camera.anim.points.rotate(30 * DEGREES, axis=RIGHT),\n"
")\n"
"self.play(FadeOut(group1))\n"
"\n"
"self.play(FadeIn(group2))\n"
"self.play(\n"
"    self.camera.anim.points.rotate(40 * DEGREES, axis=OUT),\n"
")\n"
"self.play(FadeOut(group2))"
msgstr ""

