#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:118
msgid "三维坐标"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:120
msgid "回顾如下的图片，在平面坐标中，我们提及了若干个主要的方向，包括 ``LEFT`` 、 ``RIGHT`` 、 ``DOWN`` 以及 ``UP``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:127
msgid ""
"在三维空间中，我们在第三个分量还有两个主要的方向，它们分别是 ``OUT`` 和 ``IN`` ，分别表示“离开二维平面”（即朝向初始摄像"
"机）以及“深入二维平面”（即远离初始摄像机）的方向，如下图所示："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:134
msgid "从而，我们可以利用这两个方向在三维空间中移动，当然，也可以在三维空间中旋转"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:13
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"self.camera.points.set(orientation=quat(-0.15, -0.28, -0.04, 0.95))\n"
"\n"
"# 用于辅助观察的坐标系\n"
"\n"
"axes = ThreeDAxes(\n"
"    (-3, 3), (-3, 3), (-3, 3),\n"
"    axis_config={\n"
"        'include_tip': True,\n"
"    }\n"
")\n"
"axes.z_axis.set(color=MAROON)\n"
"labels = axes.get_axis_labels(rotate_xy=False, z_kwargs={'color': MAROON})\n"
"\n"
"# 用于演示的矩形物件\n"
"\n"
"square = Square(color=BLUE, fill_alpha=0.6)\n"
"\n"
"# 动画过程\n"
"\n"
"Group(axes, labels, square).show().apply_depth_test()\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"self.play(\n"
"    square.anim(duration=1.5).points.shift(OUT * 2),\n"
"    square.anim(duration=3).points.shift(IN * 4),\n"
"    Rotate(square, PI, axis=RIGHT, about_point=ORIGIN, duration=3),\n"
"    lag_ratio=1\n"
")\n"
"self.forward()"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_scene.rst:52
msgid ":class:`~.ThreeDAxes` :meth:`~.Item.apply_depth_test` :class:`~.Rotate`"
msgstr ""

